440
00:29:11,170 --> 00:29:12,603
Right?

441
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:16,400
I'm just doing my duty.

442
00:29:17,300 --> 00:29:20,469
You guys, both of you are the same.

443
00:29:20,470 --> 00:29:22,520
So tight-lipped!

444
00:29:25,150 --> 00:29:26,969
Ai Mor.

445
00:29:26,970 --> 00:29:28,539
What did you say to him?

446
00:29:28,540 --> 00:29:30,779
He was just talking about you.

447
00:29:30,780 --> 00:29:33,229
So I just told him about you.

448
00:29:33,230 --> 00:29:35,260
