449
00:29:35,750 --> 00:29:37,029
He just yells at me, Dude.

450
00:29:37,030 --> 00:29:40,110
Did you know? On the first day, he just suddenly threw water in my face.

451
00:29:40,110 --> 00:29:42,829
And another day he just pushed me in the water. Like, damn.

452
00:29:42,829 --> 00:29:44,449
Him yelling at you, Dude...

453
00:29:44,450 --> 00:29:46,419
That's what made you like him?

454
00:29:46,419 --> 00:29:48,729
Such a Thai Lakorn. Damn.

455
00:29:48,730 --> 00:29:50,770
You're such a pain in the ass.

456
00:29:53,180 --> 00:29:55,269
- So where are you going, Dude?
- To take a piss.

457
00:29:55,269 --> 00:29:57,919
- Are you shy?
- Shy, my ass.

458
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:14,153
Hey!

459
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:17,420
What's up, Khru Doi?
[T/N: Khru = Teacher, Doi = Hill]

460
00:30:18,020 --> 00:30:20,720
Is your dad not here to protect you today?

461
00:30:27,150 --> 00:30:28,660
