462
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:30,820
To knock your head off, you son of a bitch!

463
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:33,530
You bastard!

464
00:30:35,370 --> 00:30:37,550
Do you think you're so great?

465
00:30:37,550 --> 00:30:40,220
Let go! You asshole!

466
00:30:46,180 --> 00:30:47,713
Shit! Hey!

467
00:30:49,490 --> 00:30:51,023
Run!

468
00:30:55,750 --> 00:30:57,009
Run faster!

469
00:30:57,009 --> 00:30:58,743
I know!

470
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,750
Come this way!

471
00:31:14,110 --> 00:31:16,089
I'm damn exhausted.

472
00:31:16,090 --> 00:31:19,399
I now believe that you really live up to your nickname

473
00:31:19,399 --> 00:31:21,300
Tian, the trouble magnet.

474
00:31:22,060 --> 00:31:23,470
