477
00:31:29,290 --> 00:31:34,010
I think that...those guys will definitely follow you to get back at you up there.

478
00:31:35,970 --> 00:31:38,359
Screw them. I'm not scared anymore.

479
00:31:38,360 --> 00:31:40,850
I have someone protecting me anyway.

480
00:31:41,930 --> 00:31:43,429
You got the guts to say that.

481
00:31:43,430 --> 00:31:47,440
I really want to see the face of this Chief of yours now.

482
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:53,880
[Phaphirun Unit]

483
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:54,899
Here, Dude. These are strawberries.

484
00:32:54,899 --> 00:32:56,649
Wash them with a bit of water and they're good to eat.

485
00:32:56,650 --> 00:32:58,579
They're from Pha Pun Dao, you know!

486
00:32:58,580 --> 00:33:01,290
They're organic, for sure. Trust me.

487
00:33:01,290 --> 00:33:03,569
As for these... Moo Yau.
[T/N: Sausage of pork paste that's been wrapped in banana leaf and then boiled]

488
00:33:03,569 --> 00:33:05,710
Don't eat too many, Dude.

489
00:33:07,550 --> 00:33:09,349
Dude.

490
00:33:09,350 --> 00:33:12,400
And...about what you told me last night,

491
00:33:13,360 --> 00:33:15,380
